headline: Quantum Pact: NVIDIA, Honeywell Raise Stakes for IonQ, Rigetti, D-Wave
summary: Honeywell's Quantinuum secures $600M with NVIDIA among backers, bringing IonQ, Rigetti and D-Wave into sharper investor focus.

headline: TRG Accelerates Global Leadership in Managed Endpoints and Cybersecurity
summary: CLEVELAND, September 09, 2025--TRG, the global leader in comprehensive, device-agnostic managed endpoint solutions, today announced a series of milestones that expand its reach, deepen its capabilities and deliver greater value to enterprise customers worldwide.
